{"tid":217850,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"好心您班新會然刨熟書先上黎啦 扮撚哂野咁","createTime":"2017-04-26T05:58:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T07:55:01.000Z","uid":23815,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"723c148c2799440b6865ba12667f8191ada7a124","tid":217850,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:58:49.000Z","msg":"比十蚊拎個ac 就以為自己係高登 / 連登仔 ?<br />\n遠既野唔講<br />\n最常見幾篇潮文點都要知啦掛<br />\n<br />\n入鄉隨俗 <br />\n熟讀潮文呢啲基本野啦下話<br />\n岩先有人貼ip都唔洗check<br />\n有人指出問題再紅大字叫人恥笑開始<br />\n屌您老母 我係您老母都後悔生左個低質既智障出黎<br />\n原諒我份人係咁直架啦<br />\n<br />\n您入外國藉都起碼要識唱國歌啦<br />\n高 / 連登特有文化真係唔希望比您班小學雞整到無撚左<br />\n<br />\n唔岩聽既咪唔好上黎囉<br />\n無人留您呢啲垃圾係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b56842a4964ce61d12239c0ed4cda35308373c32","tid":217850,"uid":61832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:00:17.000Z","msg":"岩你老母"},{"pid":"7e04f0fb8aca10a50537cf4c13e4d8950ada4152","tid":217850,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:02:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩你老母</blockquote><br />\n啱囉咁<br />\n屌您老母"},{"pid":"75aa97a63d8e0f4db9d9535c530e67460d88a682","tid":217850,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843261b65fce4885f26f016aa52b3e4a3307617a","tid":217850,"uid":2959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"咩post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e451e50ccceafa69c6193e8a0e4399122c4e83","tid":217850,"uid":23815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩你老母</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喂<br />\n